create_issue "Add inspect subcommand -- show WASM file size and section breakdown" "Show total file size and size of each WASM section.\n\n**Expected output:**\n\`\`\`\nFile size: 14.2 KB\nSections:\n  code: 8.1 KB\n\`\`\`\n\n**Acceptance criteria:**\n- Sizes in human-readable format\n- Test with known WASM file\n\n**PR requirements:**\n- Run \`cargo fmt\` and \`cargo clippy\` before submitting" "good first issue,wasm"
create_issue "Add --max-memory flag to cap memory usage" "Allow \`--max-memory 512000\` to set maximum memory in bytes.\n\n**Acceptance criteria:**\n- Memory limit passed to host\n- Simulation aborts with clear error if exceeded\n- Default limit documented\n\n**PR requirements:**\n- Run \`cargo fmt\` and \`cargo clippy\` before submitting" "good first issue,cli"

