create_issue "Add --events-only flag to suppress non-event output" "When \`--events-only\` set, print only diagnostic events.\n\n**Acceptance criteria:**\n- Only events printed\n- Compatible with \`--json\`\n- Test verifies suppressed output\n\n**PR requirements:**\n- Run \`cargo fmt\` and \`cargo clippy\` before submitting" "help wanted,cli,output"
create_issue "Implement SourceMapper for WASM debug symbols" "Map WASM offsets to source locations using DWARF debug info.\n\n**Background:** \`SourceMapper::new_with_options(wasm_bytes, false)\` initialises the mapper. \`mapper.has_debug_symbols()\` returns whether debug info is present. \`mapper.map_wasm_offset_to_source(0)\` returns source location.\n\n**Acceptance criteria:**\n- Source file and line shown when available\n- Falls back to offset when no symbols\n- Test: \`test_source_mapper_no_symbols_gives_no_location\`\n\n**PR requirements:**\n- Run \`cargo fmt\` and \`cargo clippy\` before submitting" "help wanted,wasm"
create_issue "Add --assert-cpu-limit flag for performance testing" "Allow \`--assert-cpu-limit 500000\` to fail if CPU usage exceeds value.\n\n**Acceptance criteria:**\n- Exit 0 if within limit\n- Exit 1 with message if over\n- Useful for CI regression testing\n\n**PR requirements:**\n- Run \`cargo fmt\` and \`cargo clippy\` before submitting" "help wanted,testing,performance"
