create_issue "Implement snapshot subcommand to save ledger state" "Save ledger entries for a contract to a JSON file.\n\n**Usage:**\n\`\`\`\nstellar-sim snapshot --rpc https://soroban-testnet.stellar.org --contract GABC... --output snapshot.json\n\`\`\`\n\n**Acceptance criteria:**\n- Downloads and serializes ledger entries\n- Output compatible with \`--ledger\` flag\n- Handles RPC errors gracefully\n\n**PR requirements:**\n- Run \`cargo fmt\` and \`cargo clippy\` before submitting" "help wanted,ledger,network"

