create_issue "Implement --simulate-auth-checks flag" "Enable strict authorisation checking during simulation.\n\n**Acceptance criteria:**\n- Auth failures produce clear error messages\n- \`--skip-auth\` disables checks\n- Test with contract requiring specific signer\n\n**PR requirements:**\n- Run \`cargo fmt\` and \`cargo clippy\` before submitting" "help wanted,soroban"
create_issue "Add --print-storage-diff to show storage changes after simulation" "Print which storage entries were created, modified, or deleted.\n\n**Expected output:**\n\`\`\`\nStorage diff:\n  CREATED:  ContractData(GABC..., \"counter\") = 1\n  MODIFIED: ContractData(GABC..., \"balance\") = 900 (was 1000)\n\`\`\`\n\n**Acceptance criteria:**\n- Created, modified, deleted entries shown\n- JSON output supported\n\n**PR requirements:**\n- Run \`cargo fmt\` and \`cargo clippy\` before submitting" "help wanted,ledger,output"
