create_issue "Implement extract_wasm_offset from error messages" "Implement \`extract_wasm_offset(error_msg: &str) -> Option<u64>\` finding hex offsets like \`@ 0x1a3c\` in error strings.\n\n**Background:** Soroban/Wasmi errors contain stack traces like:\n\`\`\`\n 0: func[42] @ 0xa3c\n\`\`\`\nSearch for \`@ 0x\` pattern and parse the following hex digits.\n\n**Acceptance criteria:**\n- Correctly extracts offset\n- Returns None when absent\n- Unit tests with sample error strings\n\n**PR requirements:**\n- Run \`cargo fmt\` and \`cargo clippy\` before submitting" "core,diagnostics"

